{"tid":638120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紋身男擸刀嘈交  3警合力制服","createTime":"2018-04-22T12:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T12:28:26.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6659b0d0f25b6bf3a1e3cf788a49513bae3d18aa","tid":638120,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/202031_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F202031_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f565bcc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍田啟田商場，下午近4時，兩名男子乘升降機到商場3樓，當抵達3樓電梯門打開時，一名金毛男子未待乘客離開便衝入升降機，雙方發生爭執。金毛男揮拳起腳打傷兩事主，事主見對方腰間藏有菜刀，於是立即離開現場，並報警求助。警員接報持盾牌到場，迅速將持刀男子按地制服。被捕男子與另外兩男均報稱受傷，一併送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n讀者馮先生表示，事發時看見商場大堂有3名警員持盾牌及伸縮警棍，正跑往Aeon，氣氛緊張，馮先生亦尾隨查看。3名警員抵達Aeon店外時，發現一名著拖鞋、有紋身的男子手持利器，坐於玻璃欄河邊，警員大喝對方「咪郁」，持刀男聞言情緒激動反抗，3名警員其後合力將他制服。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/202038_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F202038_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=300ab06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180422/58104423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F58104423&d=nBFEAOULz8l72pXpn6iQDW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=87a57135\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F58104423&h=f6f83615\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180422/58104423</a>"},{"pid":"ca98187483aba8613c094fa2fd4216152123c817","tid":638120,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"LM"}]}